Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:08.58,Dial_JP,,0,0,0,,なぞるように触れた　I’ｍ touching your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:23.37,Dial_JP2,,0,0,0,,You & (A)I　誘って今すぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.37,0:12:25.27,Dial_JP2,,0,0,0,,君だけ見てるから
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:26.53,Dial_JP2,,0,0,0,,All day all night
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:30.72,Dial_JP2,,0,0,0,,本当の気持ちはまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:33.95,Dial_JP2,,0,0,0,,見せてあげないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:38.39,Dial_JP2,,0,0,0,,Just You & (A)I　ひとつになれる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:41.84,Dial_JP2,,0,0,0,,予感がここにあるの Time goes by
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:45.20,Dial_JP2,,0,0,0,,太陽が沈まぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:49.69,Dial_JP2,,0,0,0,,遠く連れ去って
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.70,0:12:08.58,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,似轻描淡抹 I’ｍ touching your heart
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.08,0:12:23.37,Dial_CH2,,0,0,0,,You＆(A)I 此刻共赴邀约
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.37,0:12:25.27,Dial_CH2,,0,0,0,,我的眼中只映照着你
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.27,0:12:26.53,Dial_CH2,,0,0,0,,All day all night
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.20,0:12:30.72,Dial_CH2,,0,0,0,,我真正的心意
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.72,0:12:33.95,Dial_CH2,,0,0,0,,还尚未向你展露
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.68,0:12:38.39,Dial_CH2,,0,0,0,,Just You＆(A)I 融为一体
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.49,0:12:41.84,Dial_CH2,,0,0,0,,此刻已有预感 Time goes by
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.20,0:12:45.20,Dial_CH2,,0,0,0,,如永不落下的太阳
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.81,0:12:49.69,Dial_CH2,,0,0,0,,带我去远方吧
